   ]

    "import cv2\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from PIL import Image"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "376ad9dc",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Przykład 1: Lena"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "55e22e1a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.Image.Image image mode=L size=514x512 at 0x2D47225C400>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 8,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "lena = cv2.imread('Lena.jpg', cv2.IMREAD_GRAYSCALE)\n",
    "Image.fromarray(lena)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "015adbef",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Detekcja krawędzi metodą Sobela"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 21,
   "id": "8bba8365",
   "metadata": {
    "scrolled": true
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1080x360 with 3 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "#Detekcja krawędzi metodą Sobela - w kierunku X:\n",
    "sobelx = cv2.Sobel(src=lena, ddepth=cv2.CV_64F, dx=1, dy=0, ksize=3)\n",
    "\n",
    "#Detekcja krawędzi metodą Sobela - w kierunku Y:\n",
    "sobely = cv2.Sobel(src=lena, ddepth=cv2.CV_64F, dx=0, dy=1, ksize=3)\n",
    "\n",
    "#Detekcja krawędzi metodą Sobela - w kierunkach X i Y:\n",
    "sobelxy = cv2.Sobel(src=lena, ddepth=cv2.CV_64F, dx=1, dy=1, ksize=3)\n",
    "\n",
    "f, (a1, a2, a3) = plt.subplots(1, 3)\n",
    "f.set_figwidth(15)\n",
    "f.set_figheight(5)\n",
    "a1.imshow(sobelx, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a1.set_title('krawędzie o orientacji pionowej');\n",
    "a2.imshow(sobely, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a2.set_title('krawędzie o orientacji poziomej');\n",
    "a3.imshow(sobelxy, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a3.set_title('krawędzie o orientacjach pionowej i pionowej');"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bf766c9c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Detekcja krawędzi metodą Canny'ego"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 31,
   "id": "4e0f1fd9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1080x720 with 6 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "#Detekcja krawędzi metodą Canny'ego - wynik zależy od doboru wartości progów:\n",
    "f, ((a1, a2, a3), (a4, a5, a6)) = plt.subplots(2, 3)\n",
    "f.set_figwidth(15)\n",
    "f.set_figheight(10)\n",
    "\n",
    "a1.imshow(lena, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a1.set_title('obraz oryginalny')\n",
    "\n",
    "for ax, t1, t2 in zip([a2, a3, a4, a5, a6], [50, 50, 250, 20, 20], [200, 300, 300, 100, 300]):\n",
    "    ax.imshow(cv2.Canny(image=lena, threshold1=t1, threshold2 = t2), cmap='gray');\n",
    "    ax.set_title('Canny, próg dolny = {}, próg górny = {}'.format(t1, t2))"
   ]
  },

    "Detekcja krawędzi metodą Sobela"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 30,
   "id": "d4946538",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1800x1440 with 3 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "sobelx = cv2.Sobel(src=coins, ddepth=cv2.CV_64F, dx=1, dy=0, ksize=3)\n",
    "sobely = cv2.Sobel(src=coins, ddepth=cv2.CV_64F, dx=0, dy=1, ksize=3)\n",
    "sobelxy = cv2.Sobel(src=coins, ddepth=cv2.CV_64F, dx=1, dy=1, ksize=3)\n",
    "\n",
    "f, (a1, a2, a3) = plt.subplots(3, 1)\n",
    "f.set_figwidth(25)\n",
    "f.set_figheight(20)\n",
    "a1.imshow(sobelx, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a1.set_title('krawędzie o orientacji pionowej');\n",
    "a2.imshow(sobely, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a2.set_title('krawędzie o orientacji poziomej');\n",
    "a3.imshow(sobelxy, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a3.set_title('krawędzie o orientacjach pionowej i pionowej');"
   ]
  },

    "f, (a1, a2, a3) = plt.subplots(3, 1)\n",

    "\n",
    "a1.imshow(lena, cmap='gray');\n",
    "a1.set_title('obraz oryginalny')\n",
    "\n",
    "for ax, t1, t2 in zip([a1, a2, a3], [20, 50, 250], [50, 300, 500]):\n",
